  "title": "chore(examples): migrate e-commerce example to TypeScript",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis migrates the e-commerce code to TypeScript **so that the routing system is easier to implement**. TypeScript is supported by Parcel by default so there's no additional configuration needed.\r\n\r\nThe code in the widgets files don't contain explicit types so JavaScript users can still copy/paste if needed.\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\nNo changes in the UI.\r\n\r\n",
